Revision history for Net-Blossom-Server

{{$NEXT}}
    - Change mirror fetchers to stream origin bytes into a server-provided sink
      instead of returning a buffered body scalar.
    - Add a configurable maximum/default limit for server list responses.
    - Add a public storage backend conformance test helper.
    - Document storage backend implementation notes for database and filesystem
      backends.

0.001000 2026-07-07
    - Initial CPAN release.
    - Add framework-neutral Blossom server support, PSGI integration,
